{"tid":1281620,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Mnet新節目「女團回歸競賽」","createTime":"2019-07-03T10:33:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T23:17:59.000Z","uid":1086,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1de10e6e3444f1e9afbc1f4c02da5ceeedd0ec07","tid":1281620,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T10:33:58.000Z","msg":"Mnet將推出的新綜藝節目，女團6組同時回歸對決的形式。<br />\n<br />\n3日，據電視臺相關人士透露，Mnet最近正在策劃新綜藝節目《Queendom》。K-POP女團6組出演，以打破常規的正面對決來決定韓國女團&quot;Queen&quot;的競賽，某相關人士解釋說：&quot;這是女團同時回歸的對決秀&quot;。<br />\n<br />\n計劃從7月底開始拍攝，8月底播出。收看的時段是週四晚上9點。<br />\n<br />\n現在的MC熱門人選是張勝奎和演員李多熙。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e45c17b915eebb3796406f73690e627e6b623db9","tid":1281620,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T10:58:56.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"71fdc9bd3b9d7a48f308df0ab17139aee0279210","tid":1281620,"uid":7903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T10:59:44.000Z","msg":"冇三大既話冇乜睇頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31618e0619dbaf2131ad51686314739b99320afb","tid":1281620,"uid":56701,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:03:29.000Z","msg":"咪搞啦&hellip;之前試過係唔work,俾個假希望人地，其實年紀係呃唔到人，好少可以好似irene咁好彩，遲出道都紅得返！"},{"pid":"9507ec6e46ff1d7a87d29c6fed96c84862f01f92","tid":1281620,"uid":1086,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"71fdc9bd3b9d7a48f308df0ab17139aee0279210","tid":1281620,"uid":7903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T10:59:44.000Z","msg":"冇三大既話冇乜睇頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:11:57.000Z","msg":"搵三大咁乜，<br />\n搵啲細團，但有一、兩個團員好出名果啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1d65a24e6b4c2cf276967efb302e413fbae2d35","tid":1281620,"uid":7903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9507ec6e46ff1d7a87d29c6fed96c84862f01